metadata.name: Wilderness Fellowships
metadata.description: Unlock a new dimension of art with the Genesis Release of a pioneering Regenerative Art collection. Experience the dynamic blend of collectability, composability, consumability, redeemability, and transcendability through each unique, one-of-a-kind piece of dNFT Art. Immerse yourself in the beauty of regenerative arts, each with its own story to tell. A journey to the forefront of the art-world reimagined, where blockchain meets wilderness...
